# Angels Orphanage Website

## 📌 Project Overview
The Angels Orphanage Website is a multi-page website designed for a non-profit organization that supports vulnerable children. The website provides information about the orphanage, its services, and ways for the public to support or get involved.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Create an online presence for Angels Orphanage
- Provide information about services and mission
- Allow users to make enquiries
- Encourage donations and community support

---

## 🌐 Pages Included
- **Home (index.html)** – Introduction and welcome message  
- **About (about.html)** – Information about the orphanage  
- **Services (services.html)** – Services offered  
- **Products / Support (products.html)** – Ways to support (donations, sponsorship)  
- **Contact (contact.html)** – Contact details  
- **Enquiry (enquiry.html)** – Form for user messages  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML – Structure of the website  
- CSS – Styling and layout  
- JavaScript – Form handling and interactivity  

---

